    "media:imagetext": "One of the Catalinas which operate from Port Moresby to\nWest\nPapua. to East Papua and to adiacent islands to the\nnorth-east.\nA Qantas Douglas airliner at a New Guinea airport. Qantas operates\ntwelve regular services and many charter services in the \"Territory.\"\nNEW GUINEA \"BIRD OF PARADISE\" SERVICE\nINTERNAL SERVICES AND ISLANDS SERVICES\nMANUS ISLAND\nWEWAK\nWARAG\nMT HAGEN\nNONDUG'\nFINSCHHAFEN\n‹AVIENG\nRABAUL\nMURRAY\nBUKA PASSAGE\nQUINOT BAY\nKIETAI\nKEREMA\nKOKODA\nHIGATURA\nABAU\n• LOSUIA\nDEBOYNE IS\nPacifie\nOcean\nYANDINAS\nHONIAR\nCoral Sea\nCAIRNS\nAUSTRALIA\nTOWNSVILLE\nROCKH\n• ESPIRITU SANTO\nSUVA\n-VILA\nBRISBANE\nNOUMEA -\nSYDNEY\nLEGEND\nREGULAR SERVICES\nFREQUENT NON SCHEDULED FLIGHTS\nNORFOLK. ISLAND-",
